oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jimmie Dale Gilmore Labor Day Weekend Extravaganza
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Concert tours; Gilmore, Jimmie Dale; Old 97's (Musical group); Watson, Dale; Woodcuts (prints); Holidays;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and green on yellow) announcing a Labor Day Weekend Extravaganza featuring Jimmie Dale Gilmore, Old 97's and Dale Watson at the House of Blues on August 29, Rockefeller's on August 30, Deep Ellum Live on August 31, and The Backyard on September 1. Poster features a woodcut of a jockey riding a horse and the phrase "I'm goin', Are you?"
